data.description: **NEW PRICE** Welcome to your future 3bd 2bth home! The sellers has taken steps to make their home more appealing to potential buyers by establishing a new list price and added a home warranty to make the property more competitive. This warranty can provide a peace of mind to the buyer, as it typically covers certain repairs and replacements for the first year of homeownership, helping to protect their investment in case of unexpected issues. Seller is adding $1,000 allowance towards yard care.
